response.overview: In a world in which Great Britain has become a fascist state, a masked vigilante known only as “V” conducts guerrilla warfare against the oppressive British government. When V rescues a young woman from the secret police, he finds in her an ally with whom he can continue his fight to free the people of Britain.
response.tagline: People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.
response.title: V for Vendetta
